<c74object name="pnp.roughness~">

	<digest>
		Calculates the spectral roughness of an incoming audio signal
	</digest>
	
	<description>
		A rough sound is one that has an uneven or irregular sonic texture. <m>pnp.roughness~</m> calculates the apparent roughness of an incoming signal by measuring how "rough" the spectral content of the sound is.
	</description>
	
